U.S. House Speaker Nancy Pelosi has recently intimated that she intends to visit Taiwan. This has triggered a stern warning from the Chinese government. If she follows through, she'll have to bear the severe consequences of trampling on the "one-China principle" and undermining China's territorial integrity. Editor: Yuan Xin Chief editor: Ge Jing (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)